{"tid":1011104,"cid":27,"subCid":0,"title":"［TG]電影撚吹水台","createTime":"2019-02-06T13:26:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-30T04:20:28.000Z","uid":116725,"like":4,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"7e5dbb27f6c6965da5fafb768e46b923dcc53e11","tid":1011104,"uid":116725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-06T13:26:32.000Z","msg":"見連登好似無咩專講電影既吹水gp<br />\n所以開左個TG電影gp<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n入面咩關於電影既野都傾得，有興趣的話仲可以約下睇電影添，想召集一班好愛睇電影，想分享各類型電影既愛好者，不論恐怖片，愛情片，文藝，cult片，總之係鍾意電影既都可以嚟join<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n而家個gp有20幾個人，入面無厹無女神，純係電影愛好者<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/lihkgmovie\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Flihkgmovie&d=8mXO1VLy4U8nFH7Q%2FrHVYPsPRfgRtgRFNgQ5kFpanIU%3D&h=649dd369\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/lihkgmovie</a>"},{"pid":"d62e9e5a3dc984944ebe06248ae179149e9b8cf3","tid":1011104,"uid":121740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-06T13:27:10.000Z","msg":"ok"},{"pid":"0086e2f46270efe5b0acfe4c5bd620f96a620814","tid":1011104,"uid":34567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-06T14:22:52.000Z","msg":"ok"},{"pid":"35e5c7bc672cf281afbc7c8a988a2b22c280429d","tid":1011104,"uid":121740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-07T03:27:28.000Z","msg":"ok"},{"pid":"d963f41a3844899126426cc650d7fd955afec0ec","tid":1011104,"uid":128220,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-07T04:29:00.000Z","msg":"ok"},{"pid":"7542def437126aceb771d029cf599516a9d2e45e","tid":1011104,"uid":121740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-07T05:49:16.000Z","msg":"ok"},{"pid":"760dee384729887a23531db6c86f7ba71624e492","tid":1011104,"uid":34567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-07T08:14:30.000Z","msg":"